    q(28,"A game developer needs to invert a 3x3 rotation matrix R. She knows R is orthogonal. What is the fastest way?",["Row reduce [R|I]","Compute R^(-1) = R^T (just transpose)","Use the adjugate formula","Compute determinants"],"For orthogonal matrices, R^(-1) = R^T. Simply transposing is O(n^2), much faster than row reduction.",1),
